full_text: Screened by NARA, 6/1/2023 U.S. Naturalization Test U.S. History and Government Questions Due Consideration Form 2 Applicant's name: Maria Cevallos 28 8/3 252 pass: fail: A-number: Date: 11-1907 correct incorrect 1.
